elements</title>
<p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:4;26:4" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/data.dita">The following code sample shows how the <xmlelement class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlelement " xtrc="xmlelement:3;26:56" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/data.dita">data</xmlelement> element can be used to
