metadata</title><p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:5;34:20" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/data.dita">The following code sample shows how nested <xmlelement class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlelement " xtrc="xmlelement:5;34:75" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/data.dita">data</xmlelement> elements can provide
