<p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:6;50:4" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/data.dita">The following code sample contains specializations of the <xmlelement class="+ topic/keyword markup-d/markupname xml-d/xmlelement " xtrc="xmlelement:7;50:74" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/langRef/base/data.dita">data</xmlelement> element:
